  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Before Playing</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a horror game.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have a weak heart or similar conditions, please refrain from playing.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are certain scenes where the game may forcibly close as part of the experience.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are streaming, please take care to avoid showing your desktop screen or similar content.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435270/extras/8bb244725eb6716d76a24b8338d4c16a.avif?t=1770659978\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435270/extras_big/8bb244725eb6716d76a24b8338d4c16a.avif?t=1770659978 width=800 height=158 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever lost your memories?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have precious memories?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you take the first step to regain them?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if it means involving everyone around you...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z Button or Enter: Confirm  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X Button: Cancel or Open Menu Screen  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow Keys: Move Character  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift Key: Dash  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold Z Button: Fast-forward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lastly</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This work is fiction.</p>",
